- Tonnellerie Ô: A renowned company known for its high-quality Puncheon Barrels made from French oak, catering to the premium segment of the market with a focus on enhancing the flavor profiles of wines and spirits.

- The Barrel Mill: Specializing in providing a range of Puncheon Barrels made from American oak, catering to a diverse customer base looking for reliable and cost-effective barrel solutions for their aging needs.

- Nadalie USA: Focused on sustainability, Nadalie USA offers eco-friendly Puncheon Barrels made from reclaimed oak, appealing to environmentally conscious customers seeking a unique aging experience.

